<bibRefCitation author="Perkins" box="[157,351,870,893]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14" refString="Perkins, P. D. (1980). Aquatic beetles of the family Hydraenidae in the Western Hemisphere: classification, biogeography and inferred phylogeny (Insecta: Coleoptera). Quaestiones Entomologicae, 16, 3 - 554." type="journal article" year="1980">
